{"tid":589051,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)偵防危機  最高危機  重裝任務","createTime":"2018-03-11T15:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T20:23:12.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"07b10a5ff3a284d16cb8972a3ad902bb85270c0d","tid":589051,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Mc4KseLfJtuR7deRXvtNef7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9a1adba2\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Mc4KseLfJtuR7deRXvtNef7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0c25963b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/91sETTGTIDL._SL1500_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fecx.images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F91sETTGTIDL._SL1500_.jpg&h=3dd35459&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/83/ExecutiveDecision_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F83%2FExecutiveDecision_poster.jpg&h=3f3df4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/nmeshs/normal_4b68e948817d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fnmeshs%2Fnormal_4b68e948817d2.jpg&h=c49c9858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一座已經使用很久的監獄即將停用，軍官湯姆奉命監督移監。事實上，之前湯姆就已接獲線報，說這天犯人中有某些人策劃著什麼，打算來個裡應外合。<br />\n為了保險起見，湯姆便找來曾經在部隊的老搭當曼寧幫忙。犯人轉移的最後一天，所以事情都在緊張的氣氛中進行，平時躁動不安的犯人此刻更加瘋狂萬分。當晚，自稱政府轉移隊的人員混入監獄，企圖劫走了名叫薩曼莎和夏洛特的兩名女囚犯。女犯身份之謎，劫獄事件背後的陰謀，在槍林彈雨的對決中慢慢交替浮現.... <br />\n<br />\n2.一架載滿400名乘客的波音747從希臘雅典起飛前往美國華盛頓首府的途中，被一群由阿拉伯人納吉&middot;哈森帶領的恐怖份子挾持，要求美國政府釋放他們的首腦艾爾&middot;沙耶&middot;亞法，否則將在華盛頓上空引爆機上的毒氣彈，摧毀美國東岸超過四千萬條人命<br />\n<br />\n3.電影描述第三次世界大戰後城市廢墟堆裡，一個使用英語的國家成為以社會主義、高科技、專制特色統治的有秩序國家，認為人類社會的亂象皆源自於「感覺」，因此以藥物 Prozium 麻痺人類的感情和感覺，探討「高科技侵犯人性人權」的哲學電影<br />\n<br />\n12 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Mc4KseLfJtuR7deRXvtNef7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7fcb96ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Mc4KseLfJtuR7deRXvtNef7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c9f2ec13\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f7d73a2e95917c99414877f835f313daa5a709","tid":589051,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1020d1ffe8dcaa23c3162ce684228d30465a886d","tid":589051,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156d97ab3bed6b0d7a4